quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,6,"ЖЉum ko Men jaЕ‹tanii on -immorde e fuЙ—Й—oode tagu mo'on e taaЙ“e mu'un e alhaaliiji Й“en Й“e no jibinee e mo'on- fii yo on gomЙ—in wonndema On Alla TaguЙ—o on ko Kanko woni Goonga ka sikke alaa e muuЙ—um, Й—um no lunndii ko rewoton kon immorde e sanamuuji mo'on, fii yo on gomЙ—in wonnde Kanko himo wurnita mayЙ“e Й“en, wonnde Kanko e dow kala huunde ko O HattanЙ—o, hay e huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  22,7,"Fii yo on gomЙ—in wonnde pellet, Darngal ngal ko aroowal sikkewoo alaa fii arugol maggal, wonnde pellet, Alla immintinay maayЙ“e Й“en ka genaale maЙ“Й“e fii yo O yoЙ“u Й“e e dow golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  22,8,"No e heeferЙ“e Й“en on mo no wennja fii Ngootimpaaku Alla ngun, ko aldaa e ganndal hewtinayngal Й“e e Goonga kan, wanaa jokkooЙ“e feewuЙ“e tinndinay Й“e Й“e e Й—um, wanaa kadi deftere jalbinnde jippinaande immorde ka Alla fewnaynde Й“e e Goonga kan."
  22,9,"Ko o falЙ—o daande makko sabu mawnintinaare fii yo o yiltu yimЙ“e Й“en e gomЙ—inal e naatugol ngol ka diina Alla, kala mo sifa mu'un wa'i nii no woodani mo koyeere ka aduna sabu lepte hawrayЙ—e e makko Й—en, Men mettina mo kadi ka Laakara Lepte Yiite sunnooje Й—en."
  22,10,"Wi'anee mo: "ЖЉen Lepte Й—e meeЙ—Й—aa Й—um ko sabu ko faggitinoЙ—aa kon immorde e keefeeru e geddi Й—en, Alla O Leptataa hay e gooto e tagu Makko ngun si wanaa sabu bakkaatu"."
  22,11,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en powotooЙ—o himo rewa Alla e dow sikke, si moЖґЖґere heЙ“ii mo immorde e cellal e ngalu o tamoo e dow gomЙ—inal makko e dewal makko Alla ngal, si jarrabuyee hiЙ“ii mo sabu Г±aw e baasal o Г±akkinora diina makko kan o yartodina e makka, o hayrii aduna makko on, keeferaaku makko ngun Й“eydataa mo ngeЙ—o ngu winndana- nanooka mo ka aduna, o hayririi kadi Laakira mak- ko on sabu ko o hawrata kon immorde e Lepte Alla ko Й—um tigi woni hayrere Й“anngunde nden."
  22,12,"Himo rewa gaanin Alla sanamuuji Й—i lorrataa mo si o yeddii Й—i, Й—i nafataa mo kadi si o Й—oftike Й—i, ngal dewal sanamuuji Й—i lorrataa Й—i nafataa kadi ko Й—um woni majjere woЙ—Й—unde nden gaayi Goonga kan."
  22,13,"Oo keefeero wonЙ—o rewude sanamuuji Й—in, himo rewa kon ko lorra mu'un heЙ“ii ka kan Й“uri Й“adaade diini nafa mu'un haЙ—taaka kan, pellet, bonii on reweteeЙ—o mo lorra mu'un Й“uri Й“adaade diini nafa mo'on, bonii walloowo wonannde on wallitorЙ—o mo, bonii wonndiiЙ—o kadi wonannde on wonndiniiЙ—o e makko."
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla hiMo naada Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Mo Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe Й—en Aljannaaji canЙ—i Й—in no ila e ley kuЙ“eeji majji, pellet, Alla hiMo wada ko o faalaa kon immorde e Yurminngol on mo O Yurmini Й—um, e Leptugol on mo O Lepti Й—um, alaa dooloowo Mo O Senike."
  22,15,"On laatiiЙ—o himo sikki wonnde Alla wallataa Annabaajo makko on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) ka aduna e ka Laakara awa yo o fontu Й“oggol faade ka kippudi suudu makko, refti o Й—eЙ—Й—itora ngol wenngugol hoore-makko gaayi leydi ndin, refti o ndaara taw si Й—um ittay tikkere nde o tawata nden ka wonkii makko, Alla ko O walloowo Annabaajo Makko on, sanndalЙ—iiЙ—o on jaЙ“i wllo o saliima."